Privacy Policy

Effective Date: September 18, 2025

This game is designed to be lightweight, distraction-free, and safe for all users, including children.

Information We Collect

We do not collect, store, or share any personal information.
	•	No accounts or registration are required.
	•	No location data is collected.
	•	No internet, Bluetooth, or local network access is used.
	•	No analytics or third-party tracking tools are included.

How the App Works

The game runs entirely on your Apple Watch. All interactions, game progress, and feedback remain on your device. Nothing is transmitted or stored externally.

Children’s Privacy

This app is safe for children. Since no personal data is collected, there is no risk of misuse of children’s information.

Contact Us

